public class MainFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.lang.Cloneable
This is main controller of the overall frame. It provides view switching method goto, view update method and stores current logged client's information.

    • goTo

      public void goTo​(java.lang.String name)
      This function used to switch view. Two switch mode: Index, enroll, function view switch uses this switch mode, other view switch use FunctionController.goTo(String)

      Views loaded on demand. The view will be created by ControllerFactory if list doesn't have this view.

      参数:
      name - the view name which will be switched to
